snippet.title: THE BENGAL FILES Official Trailer | Vivek Agnihotri | Abhishek A | Pallavi J | Zee Studios | 5 Sept
snippet.description:
From the makers of The Kashmir Files and The Tashkent Files, here is the official trailer of THE BENGAL FILES, the powerful conclusion to the trilogy by two-time National Award-winning filmmaker Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri.

A presentation by: Tej Narayan & Snehlatha Agarwal and I Am Buddha

Directed by: Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri
Produced by: Abhishek Agarwal, Pallavi Joshi and Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri 
Worldwide Release: Zee Studios
Music: Zee Music Co.
Starring: Mithun Chakraborty, Anupam Kher, Pallavi Joshi, Darshan Kumaar, Simratt Kaur

This September, witness the untold truth of the Hindu genocide.

#TheBengalFiles #RightToLife

snippet.title: Rao Bahadur | Teaser | Satya Dev | Venkatesh Maha | GMB | SriChakraas | A+S | Summer 2026
snippet.description:
Rao Bahadur is a psychological drama set against the backdrop of a fading aristocracy - Made in Telugu, for the world.
 
Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Venkatesh Maha and starring the versatile Satya Dev as Rao Bahadur, the film is presented by Superstar Mahesh Babu & Namrata Shirodkar‚Äôs GMB Entertainment and produced by A+S Movies and SriChakraas Entertainments.
 
Releasing Summer 2026, in Theaters worldwide.
 
Genre - Psychological Drama, Suspense, Dark Comedy, Magical Realism.
 
 
Cast and Crew Details:

Welcome to my channel!
I create Mashup, Fan-Made, and Concept Trailers by combining and editing footage from one or multiple movies. These trailers offer a fresh take on existing films, reimagine stories, or even create entirely new movie concepts.
Mashup trailers are a creative way to change the genre, storyline, or focus of a film. For example, a comedy can be transformed into a thriller, or different movies can be combined to create a crossover that doesn‚Äôt exist. These edits allow fans to see their favorite actors and films in a whole new light.
By mixing and re-editing scenes, I aim to build excitement for upcoming releases, highlight unique ideas, and bring cinematic "what-if" scenarios to life. Since these are creative remixes, they may be protected under fair use.

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)
snippet.description:
Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)

DISCLAIMER: I am CHEATING! (Technically)

I am using mods that are not allowed in official leaderboard speedruns. This is practice for my videos, not for world records! I am also simulating ender eye calculation using a mod, I am only throwing the eyes to simulate a time spend, as official speedrunners use a bot to calculate the stronghold location off of 1/2 ender eyes.

I am also using no fog, optifine zoom, increased pearl rates (matching 1.16 rates), and a custom f3 menu with Nether Coordinates. (And maybe more, idk, who cares)
